755
00:48:40,884 --> 00:48:42,790
Ollie. Please.

756
00:48:48,415 --> 00:48:51,837
Some target shooting.
State champion in '94.

757
00:48:52,307 --> 00:48:54,509
- You're crazy if you go out there!
- Let us pass!

758
00:48:54,704 --> 00:48:56,131
Let us pass, please!

759
00:48:56,156 --> 00:48:57,242
Let's just talk this thing through.

760
00:48:57,267 --> 00:48:59,428
