00:49:07,227 --> 00:49:09,354
You've already psyched out
half a dozen of my people already.

765
00:49:09,379 --> 00:49:10,368
Your people?

766
00:49:10,393 --> 00:49:12,548
What kind of talk is that?
They're people, that's all.

767
00:49:12,573 --> 00:49:14,033
Now... now listen, everyone.

768
00:49:14,034 --> 00:49:17,082
We are experiencing some kind of disaster.

769
00:49:17,118 --> 00:49:18,964
I don't know whether
it's man-made or natural,

770
00:49:18,998 --> 00:49:23,839
but I do know that it's definitely
not supernatural or biblical,

771
00:49:23,853 --> 00:49:25,304
and, no offense, Mrs. Carmody,

772
00:49:25,329 --> 00:49:29,001
but the only way we're gonna
help ourselves is to seek rescue.

773
00:49:30,762 --> 00:49:31,908
We're going out.

774
00:49:34,289 --> 00:49:36,348
- Brent, look.
- I'm not discussing this any further.

775
00:49:36,373 --> 00:49:38,681
