776
00:49:40,243 --> 00:49:41,733
Tie this around your waist.

777
00:49:42,396 --> 00:49:43,086
What for?

778
00:49:43,111 --> 00:49:45,415
It'll let us know 
you got at least 300 feet.

779
00:49:47,524 --> 00:49:48,720
I'll do it.

780
00:49:49,987 --> 00:49:51,633
Are you throwing in with them?

781
00:49:51,658 --> 00:49:53,329
Me? No thanks.

782
00:49:53,710 --> 00:49:56,523
I think your man there
is a little too tightly wound.

783
00:49:56,548 --> 00:49:58,290
Gonna get somebody killed.

784
00:49:58,541 --> 00:50:01,572
But I'm thinkin' we could use
that shotgun of yours.

785
00:50:01,915 --> 00:50:04,076
