when I pulled in.

786
00:50:04,322 --> 00:50:06,311
Red pickup, right? Far entrance?

787
00:50:06,555 --> 00:50:08,546
Son, you got brass balls.

788
00:50:09,400 --> 00:50:11,149
The shells are in the glove compartment.

789
00:50:11,174 --> 00:50:12,392
Drive it back.

790
00:50:14,470 --> 00:50:17,701
All right. 
Just see they're paying out this line.

791
00:50:17,726 --> 00:50:21,440
Line's up, I'll cut her loose,
just so you understand.

792
00:50:21,465 --> 00:50:22,493
Yeah.

793
00:50:30,171 --> 00:50:32,503
You sure there's no way
I can talk you out of this?

794
00:50:32,833 --> 00:50:37,733
David, there's nothing out there. 
Nothing in the mist.

795
00:50:38,211 --> 00:50:39,923
What if you're wrong?

796
00:50:40,781 --> 00:50:42,587
Then, I guess...

797
00:50:44,474 --> 00:50:47,681
...the joke would be on me after all.

798
00:50:52,783 --> 00:50:54,400
We're gonna send back help.

799
00:50:55,206 --> 00:50:57,538
You'll die out there. All of you.

800
00:51:10,487 --> 00:51:13,456
Hey, crazy lady, I believe in God too.

801
00:51:13,481 --> 00:51:17,504
I just don't think he's the bloodthirsty
asshole you make him out to be.

802
00:51:17,529 --> 00:51:20,352
Well, you take that up with the devil
when you run into him.

803
00:51:20,377 --> 00:51:22,048
You just chat it over at your leisure.

804
00:51:30,620 --> 00:51:32,991
Well, let's strike out toward 
the center of town.

805
00:51:51,959 --> 00:51:53,272
Keep it loose.

806
00:52:09,129 --> 00:52:11,679
Nice and easy. Keep going.

807
00:52:29,726 --> 00:52:30,715
Look.

808
00:52:33,935 --> 00:52:35,072
It's going.

809
00:52:37,023 --> 00:52:38,183
They're doing good.

810
00:52:56,039 --> 00:52:57,267
Put it down!

811
00:52:59,635 --> 00:53:00,597
Pull!

812
00:53:02,323 --> 00:53:05,111
Oh, my God! I'm slippin'!

813
00:53:06,416 --> 00:53:08,748
Pull! Back up! Back up!
Back up!

814
00:53:22,243 --> 00:53:23,232
Get it off!

815
00:53:32,576 --> 00:53:33,757
Oh, my God.

816
00:53:40,283 --> 00:53:41,750
- Aw, sh...
- Blood!

817
00:53:41,818 --> 00:53:43,547
Awww, sh...

818
00:53:43,572 --> 00:53:45,233
Oh, my God!

819
00:53:47,892 --> 00:53:48,991
Oh, my God!

820
00:54:03,702 --> 00:54:04,763
Cut the rope!

821
00:54:07,344 --> 00:54:08,537
Shut the door!

822
00:54:14,084 --> 00:54:16,357
Now do you see?

823
00:54:18,088 --> 00:54:19,912
Now do you believe?

824
00:54:28,989 --> 00:54:31,331
About a half-hour of daylight left.

825
00:54:32,331 --> 00:54:34,148
Guys, how's it going
with these work lights?

826
00:54:34,173 --> 00:54:35,925
We're gettin' 'em rigged up all right.

827
00:54:36,329 --> 00:54:37,758
Yeah, check it out.

828
00:54:38,136 --> 00:54:40,308
All right, all right. Save it, save it.

829
00:54:40,730 --> 00:54:42,448
These batteries ain't topped up.

830
00:54:42,589 --> 00:54:44,564
